  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The patient presents to the ophthalmological emergencies and / or to the internal medicine&#xD;
      department. NOIA clinical discovery Patient referred in radiology for brain and visual MRI.&#xD;
      The two sequences added by the research (8 minutes) will be added to that of the treatment.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
